M|Note|ln|** Always editorial tone. Never discount or urgency language. Captions are often 1-2 sentences only.
M|Note|**So|** Visual-first platform. Reels for reach, carousels for saves. Hashtags: niche fashion + aesthetic tags, not mass (#fashion, #style).
M|Note|ro|** Meta + Instagram ad primary. Lookalike audience from existing cs. Exclude bargain-hunter interest segments.
M|Note|at|** Mood: clean, minimal, editorial. Natural light preferred. No busy backgrounds. Think editorial magazine spread.
M|Note|ka|** Key anomaly threshold: IG ER drop > 20% WoW = flag immediately.
M|Note|fx|** E-commerce md. Track ROAS on every paid cg. AOV is the key rv lever.